## Homepage ([Home.tsx](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/Home.tsx))

Seven scroll-animated sections using `IntersectionObserver`:

1. **Hero** — Full-viewport with animated gradient bg, gold "Design Intelligence" heading, V5 badge, floating stat cards (578K+, 150+, 38), dual CTAs
2. **Features** — 6 glassmorphism cards: AI Design Brief, Live Cost Calculator, Investor PDF, MIYAR Score, Market Intelligence, Sustainability
3. **How It Works** — 4-step timeline: Define → Analyze → Score → Export
4. **Trust Signals** — DLD Data, Estidama/Al Sa'fat, RICS NRM with stats
5. **App Preview** — 3D-perspective dashboard mockup with fake sidebar, KPIs, and chart
6. **Version Changelog** — V5→V1 timeline with feature lists, V5 highlighted as current
7. **Footer** — 3-column layout with brand, product links, market coverage

Includes [AnimatedCounter](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/Home.tsx#27-64) component for number-counting animation and [AnimatedSection](file:///Users/amrosaleh/Maiyar/miyar-v2/client/src/pages/Home.tsx#65-93) wrapper for scroll reveals.

